            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="HealthyLifestyle-box" style="background-color: rgb(55, 0, 113); border-radius: 4%;">
                    <img src="./images/HealthyLifestyle.png" alt="HealthyLifestyleLogo">
                <h2 style="color: white;">Healthy Lifestyle</h2>
                <div class="HealthyLifestyle-details" style="color: white;" ><ul>
                    <p>Healthy Lifestyle</p> <p>Today</p> <p><h2 style="color: white;">8 </h2></p><p>of Sleep</p><p>This section provides to the user Fitness details</p><p>
